# Title: EvilNum APT Golden Chickens Deployment Via OCX Files
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2020-07-10
# Level: critical
# Description: Detects Golden Chickens deployment method as used by Evilnum and described in ESET July 2020 report
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218.011, detection.emerging-threats
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-emerging-threats/2020/TA/Evilnum/proc_creation_win_apt_evilnum_jul20.yml

CommandLine="*regsvr32*" CommandLine="*/s*" CommandLine="*/i*" CommandLine="*\\AppData\\Roaming\\*" CommandLine="*.ocx*"